text: Hansa Session is a acoustic and string quartet extended play made by Chvrches, The songs are from their third album Love Is Dead. The Hansa Session EP was released on 16 November 2018 as digital download and on 14 December 2018 as a limited edition 10" vinyl. ==Track listing== ==References== Category:Chvrches albums Category:2018 EPs
title: Hansa Session
